{"tid":1477441,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【逆權運動】韓團GOT7港騷宣佈延期 護旗手Jackson掀罵戰累隊友","createTime":"2019-08-16T06:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:29:06.000Z","uid":74065,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5afe1c7167776e4729e5559d0a45fde8fc961dca","tid":1477441,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190816/large/1565935701_9ed6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190816%2Flarge%2F1565935701_9ed6.jpg&h=c45e30dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGOT7本月31日及下月1日舉行的港騷宣佈<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">延期</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190816/large/1565935716_a430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190816%2Flarge%2F1565935716_a430.jpg&h=60d523dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日因「反送中」問題在香港持續發生示威及遊行活動，原定不少韓團或韓星都來港開騷，不過不少藝人都接連宣佈取消來港開騷，繼《與神同行》男星朱智勛、韓國男團EXO的中國成員Lay（張藝興）及限定男團Wanna One出身的男星姜丹尼爾宣佈取消或延期來港開騷後，原定本月31日及下月1日在亞博館開騷的韓國男團GOT7今日亦宣佈延期舉行演唱會。<br />\n<br />\nGOT7主辦單位尚典娛樂集團有限公司 (REG) 今日就在Facebook宣佈「GOT7 2019 WORLD TOUR &lsquo;KEEP SPINNING&rsquo; IN HONG KONG」演唱會因目前香港社會環境上不能預測的因素宣佈延期，並表示：「以致可影響歌迷往返演唱會場地，因首先考慮到觀看演唱會觀眾們的安全，原定於2019年8月31日（星期六）及9月1日（星期日）亞洲國際博覽館Arena舉行之GOT7 2019 WORLD TOUR &lsquo;KEEP SPINNING&rsquo; IN HONG KONG 將會延期舉行。」<br />\n<br />\nGOT7的香港成員Jackson（王嘉爾）日前在微博留言自稱「我是護旗手」，表態支持中國政府的立場，當時有香港網民直言對Jackson感到失望，又有人號召網民到時去機場接Jackson機。指事件亦引起韓國網民關注，韓國網民留言：「Jackson唔係香港人嗎？似乎拋棄不了中國市場而要拋棄自己出生嘅地方嗎？」、「睇嚟生存果然係最重要嘅」等，未知是否受有關事件影響！"},{"pid":"0b31c1bdf7d16fa5b41382f9ca4cbc84b9335539","tid":1477441,"uid":74065,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:26:47.000Z","msg":"延期即係重有機會接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ab7321de0bc721b85ae2a5117349c5cf06cd4c","tid":1477441,"uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />接機 接機 接機"},{"pid":"2e0c99f82268df8ce31d5b18d1032874808d8f28","tid":1477441,"uid":240447,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母蝗加爾一個累全家<br />\n不得好死<br />\n落地獄俾狗姦"},{"pid":"f0959467c9fad2b43ac28fff10916a9152474493","tid":1477441,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:27:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190816&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59938712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190816%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59938712&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=403c896a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190816%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59938712&h=c67086af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190816&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59938712</a><br />\n<br />\n補link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de7d4a8d4b033bd0f6eb30a6bbf1437028fe853","tid":1477441,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"撳錢策略：撳完再入，入完再撳 (港幣呀！) = 癱瘓貨幣基礎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1475945/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1475945/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d049d22545c86934d568ea4207fc778aa5cc0989","tid":1477441,"uid":74065,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"2e0c99f82268df8ce31d5b18d1032874808d8f28","tid":1477441,"uid":240